data.text:
Darlington Borough Council, GB Waste Management Booking

The borough's Household Waste Recycling Centre requires an online appointment for each drop-off. Darlington residents book 15-minute appointments up to two weeks in advance. The facility requires proof of appointment and residency prior to entrance. Reservations are limited to waste that cannot be safely stored at residences. Borough officials established the online appointment system as part of their COVID-19 reopening efforts.
